<br>
Places like guk used to be amazing fun, getting groups there was pretty easy, made a lot of friends, and had a really great time.<br>
<br>
Once kunark came out, and the nerf after nerf after nerf that the class was subjected to in the name of 'balance' drove myself and countless others to abandon the class and create a rogue.<br>
<br>
Casters are as good as dead in EQ. Magicians are nothing but COH/Mod rod mules, and the 'masters of undead' more commonly known as the Necromancer are now feared for theyre manapumping abilities.<br>
<br>
